Located in the Silo area of campus. Apparently open M-F 9-4. There is a free air pump outside the door if your bike tire ever goes flat.

attachment:bikebarn.jpg

They will give you tools so you can fix your bike there, or you can turn your bike in to the bike barn staff, and they will fix it for you for a fee.  
They also sell various items you'll need for your bike like fenders, lights, and funny bike baskets.
Too bad, you can't charge purchases made there to your ["Reg Card"].
